topic.body:
US city abandons CV Drones, Apple tells Germany to change its contract tracing plans, and Bill Gates plays politician and scientist in a single interview. Also online education has forced people to sign up for creepy online proctoring services.

1588519592_1GJc2vm4vJjAKsFoFJ2D3gGmKiRac.body: COVID-19 is a hoax. The tests are not testing for covid-19. Get it through your head. The designer of the test stated that it is not testing for covid-19 therefore all this shit is low IQ waste of time.

> [anonops7](#comment_3_1JcwRQXC7dv2FhRNr44Kzm3tEAJjLiPde4): How are you so sure arione?

When I will have more time I will go over the material and give you more details.

> [amvu](#comment_1_17gKzzC9Sdp9sKsmxuferJqQXcwAYPpmd6): There is a lot of evidence showing otherwise, a huge number of geneticists working to find a reliable vaccine and a huge number of deaths. Please, provide sources for your statement.

Absolutely everything relies on the fact that people assume COVID-19 tests are testing for covid. Start by explaining why almost no healthy person died of covid but always those with serious health issues. How come covid solved all those other health issues because people don't die from other diseases like cancer, hiv, heart attacks? 

Why EU chief scientist stepped down recently saying 'he doesn't believe in the system anymore'? those scientists you mention - who is paying their salaries? 

Your top google news suggestions might not be the best. Dig dipper and you might just see why they salivate now over getting people to use mobile apps like 'contact'. Why there was so much talk for years about dollar soon collapsing and why the stock markets blame covid-19 already. You can go further and ask why American army is stationed in eastern europe for so long now and why US NATO try so hard to provoke Russia in to war in europe? They failed as Russians didn't want to fall for the provocation yet us army has no reason to stay there.

Why 80's computer geek Bill Gates now owns patent now for a virus and why he has so much in WHO, a man with no medical education who wants to make billions on vaccinating the world?

Why YouTube Wojcicki said she will censor everybody who questions official story on the pandemic? Why so many political and Silicon Valley people are related through families or close connections to each other? And it goes on and on and on.

Why the very creator of the COVID-19 test said himself that his test cannot be used for covid-19? 
Example: [US doctors virologists question current situation](https://www.bitchute.com/video/bU8XWFlo8cNN/)
